    CCOpt+: -DACCELERATE -msse2 -maes

Library testlib
  Path:         tests/
  Modules:      Notest, Hmac_tests, Dsa_tests, Testlib
  Install:      false
  Build$:       flag(tests)
  BuildDepends: nocrypto, oUnit

